          <li><a href="/profit-calculator/">Profit Calculator</a> -- Quickly calculate your total profit or loss from a crypto trade including fees.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="hub-backlink"><a href="/calculators/profit-loss/">← All Profit & Loss calculators</a></p>

      </div>
